# Tham Chiếu -- Reference
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "Tham Chiếu"

msgid "Mode"
msgstr "Chế Độ"

msgid "Draw Mode"
msgstr "Chế Độ Vẽ"

msgid "Panel"
msgstr "Bảng"

msgid ":menuselection:`Toolbar --> Tools --> Draw Tools --> Draw`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`Toolbar --> Tools --> Draw Tools --> Draw`"

msgid "The Draw tool allows you to draw free-hand strokes."
msgstr "The Draw tool allows you to draw free-hand strokes."

# Sử Dụng -- Usage
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Sử Dụng"

msgid "Selecting a Brush and Material"
msgstr "Selecting a Brush and Material"

msgid "In the Tool Settings select the brush and material to use with the tool. The Draw tool uses *Draw Brush* types. See :ref:`grease-pencil-draw-common-options` for more information."
msgstr "In the Tool Settings select the brush and material to use with the tool. The Draw tool uses *Draw Brush* types. See :ref:`grease-pencil-draw-common-options` for more informationTùy Chọn Chung -- Common Optionsettings select the brush and material to use with the tool. The Draw tool uses *Draw Brush* types. See :ref:`grease-pencil-draw-common-options` for more information."

msgid "Common Brush Options"
msgstr "Common Brush Options"

msgid "You can also configure the brush main settings exposed on the Tool Settings for convenience. For the draw brushes configuration and settings see: :doc:`Draw Brush </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/brushes/draw_brush>`."
msgstr "You can also configure the brush main settings exposed on the Tool Settings for convenience. For the draw brushes configuration and settings see: :doc:`Draw Brush </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/brushes/draw_brush>`."

msgid "Free-hand Drawing"
msgstr "Free-hand Drawing"

msgid "Click and hold :kbd:`LMB` or use the pen tip to make free-hand drawing on the viewport."
msgstr "Click and hold :kbd:`:kbd:`NCT (LMB)`` or use the pen tip to make free-hand drawing on the viewport."

msgid "Drawing free-hand strokes."
msgstr "Drawing free-hand strokes."

msgid "Stabilizer"
msgstr "Stabilizer"

msgid ":kbd:`Shift-LMB` toggle the use of :ref:`Stabilizer <grease-pencil-draw-brushes-stabilizer>` on the brush to have more control while drawing and obtain smoother lines."
msgstr ":kbd:`:kbd:`Shift-NCT (LMB)`` toggle the use of :ref:`Stabilizer <grease-pencil-draw-brushes-stabilizer>` on the brush to have more control while drawing and obtain smoother lines."

msgid "Drawing strokes using Stabilizer."
msgstr "Drawing strokes using Stabilizer."

# Đường Thẳng -- Straight Lines
msgid "Straight Lines"
msgstr "Đường Thẳng"

msgid ":kbd:`Alt-LMB` Constrains the drawing of the strokes to horizontal or vertical straight lines."
msgstr ":kbd:`:kbd:`Alt-NCT (LMB)`` Constrains the drawing of the strokes to horizontal or vertical straight lines."

msgid "Switching to the Erase Tool"
msgstr "Switching to the Erase Tool"

msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` changes temporally to the active erase tool. see :doc:`Erase Tool </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/erase>` for more information."
msgstr ":kbd:`:kbd:`Ctrl-NCT (LMB)`` changes temporally to the active erase tool. see :doc:`Erase Tool </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/erase>` for more information."

msgid "You can also use :kbd:`B` to delete all the points in the selected drawing area."
msgstr "You can also use :kbd:`:kbd:`B`` to delete all the points in the selected drawing area."

